{"tid":2283674,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Nio會唔會步Theranos 後塵","createTime":"2020-11-12T18:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T06:17:21.000Z","uid":4050,"like":126,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b31976806839539de558ee6bc9a7c31234909f","tid":2283674,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"Theranos : Elizabeth Holmes推出的「革命性驗血裝置」，號稱僅需指尖採血，就能完成 300 多項血液偵測項目，最終揭穿是一場騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTheranos實際係真係整左部驗血機出黎，而且喺walgreen到用，但發現部機勁廢，聲稱驗300種最後驗得10種， 部機出既醫療數據仲要極唔準，求其出假數據出假report<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNio: 支那電動車先峰，最近有7000架訂單，富途牛牛上面好多人講話大陸好多人揸。比tesla差電更快既換電站加上同tesla可以一戰既電池技術，luxury車箱， 仲有自家研發既自動駕駛系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評： 會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評： 唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ee9923ad745ef492b170f61f1c1bf739cbb0fa","tid":2283674,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T18:14:58.000Z","msg":"大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8240a326cfa9e9745bf06fbbd0666640065471e","tid":2283674,"uid":311726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"有人真心長渣架咩<br />\n<br />\n利申：支那不了"},{"pid":"f7b85995c8c97d46ad365c88d7cbcd1b7248f2a1","tid":2283674,"uid":147010,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/181/4e7/1814e73f3877896bd25e21e5ef61d3aa66b12c0b_b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F181%2F4e7%2F1814e73f3877896bd25e21e5ef61d3aa66b12c0b_b.png&h=404db664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78d580d2f2107ceec67a1ff7da35f96ea828a2a4","tid":2283674,"uid":286928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"